      %p To include a blockquote, wrap <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> around <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;small&gt;</code> tags. Use the <code>&lt;small&gt;</code> element to cite your source and you'll get an em dash <code>&amp;mdash;</code> before it.
